display_long_description:
# These Vehicles are… STUPID!

**Speed** them up and **Slow** them down using Hand Tracking or Controllers. But be careful, these vehicles can’t stop… if there’s a collision, it’s all over. Designed to be one of the most challenging **"One More Go"** games around.
[media]
Perfect for casual players, but also offering optional challenges for the purists.
Easy Adjustable playing position  gets you right down into the action.
For a more immersive experience, try Mixed Reality Mode.

- 7 Unique Challenging Levels.
[media]
- Cruise Control - Fill the Cruise Control Meter for a special reward.
[media]
- Mixed Reality Mode	
- Hand Tracking	
[media]																							
- Cute, polished art style and animations
- Catchy original soundtrack
- Simple easy to learn gameplay
- Unique, challenging levels
- Adjustable playing position
[media]
- Leaderboards to compete with the world or friends
- 10 achievements for those perfectionists looking for an extra challenge
- With great risk, comes great reward. Play with “Turbo” and “Overtake” modes.
[media]
